          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen loading="lazy" title="Richard Wagner: Duet iz opere Lohengrin"></iframe>
        <h4>Richard Wagner: Duet iz opere Lohengrin</h4>
        <h5>Pojeta Juan Spiwak in Maria Jeritza. Posneto na Dunaju 1908.</h5>
        <br>
